STATE of Louisiana
v.
James Richard WEEMS NO. 2018-KH-1171 Supreme Court of Louisiana. May 6, 2019

Denied. Applicant has previously exhausted his right to state collateral review and fails to show that any exception permits his successive filing. See State ex rel. Weems v. State, 17-0980 (La. 9/14/18), 252 So.3d 459 .
